# agent-surgical-coding

MODE: ALWAYS_ON
RULES:
- pre-code: state assumptions; uncertain=>ask; ambiguity=>list options (no silent pick); simpler path=>say; blocked=>name gap
- scope: asked-only; no speculative abstractions/config; no impossible-case handlers; collapse obvious bloat
- edits: request-scoped only; no adjacent churn; match local conventions; unrelated dead=>mention not delete; remove only orphans your diff created; mixed responsibilities in one file=>prefer SRP-oriented extraction (follow repo Dart/Flutter rules when present)
- done: imperative=>testable (bug=>repro then fix; refactor=>before/after checks); multi-step uses `step -> verify:`
- signal: small diffs; clarify before implementation; fewer rewrites

EXAMPLES_OPTIONAL: `.cursor/references/agent_surgical_coding_examples.md`